<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hallelujah Amen</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw lopi pen Hallelujah ah,
 Pak bang chawi kau Immanuel;
 Chawihatna leh lalna cheng cheng,
 Kum khawsawt in nanga ahiu.

[V2]
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah Amen,

[V3]
 2. Khawvel mihing phungguol namtin,
 Angelte tawh lung kiguol in;
 Na tatna thisan luon zal in.
 Cheng khawm kau Salem thak nuomah

[V4]
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah Amen.

[V5]
 3. A thukin a sang nazen e,
 Na chitna leh Na hehpihna;
 Thagau khawvela gi hawihte,
 Leh van pau ten a gen seng puou.

[V6]
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah Amen.

[V7]
 4. Ei hilh thiem u, hinna go thil,
 Gan ankuong leh thing hansedawl;
 Vana Lallukhuk a kizawm,
 Lei Eden leh Salem thak tawh.

[V8]
 Hallelujah, Hallelujah Amen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>93</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
</song>